version 0.99.2

    o Code and man files are now limited to 80 character width per line

    o Code now uniformly uses 4-space indentation

    o Vignette now uses BiocStyle style

version 0.99.1

    o fixes a bug that gave an error when plotting with idiogram=TRUE. 
      This was due to an update in the ggbio package that broke CAFE

    o CAFE can now be used with species other than human
      It is no longer limited to 22 autologous chromosomes